  <!-- Applications -->
  <h2 id="applications">Applications</h2>
  <p>
    The <strong>Alfa Laval MAB-104</strong> is a purifier type disc-stack centrifuge. It is designed to separate water (moisture) and fine sediment from mineral oil and lubricating oil. It is primarily used for purifying fuels such as <a href="/diesel-centrifuge/">diesel</a>, kerosene, etc. The MAB-104 is also used for separating water and fine sediment from <a href="/lube-oil-centrifuge/">lubrication oil</a>, <a href="/hydraulic-oil-centrifuge/">hydraulic oil</a>, and other mineral oil.
  </p>
  <p>
